BBEX3.D.TMM.USD.CA.AC.000: Exchange rates for the US dollar in Turkmenistan / USD 1 = TMM ... (middle)
General: The manat is pegged to the US dollar. Currency conversion with effect from 1 January 2009 at the rate of TMM 5,000 = TMT 1.
Source: Central Bank of Turkmenistan, Ashgabat.
Comment on 2008-01-01: On 1 January 2008, the fixed exchange rate with the US dollar was changed from USD 1 = TMM 5,200 to USD 1 = TMM 6,250; calculated devaluation: 16.8%.
Comment on 2008-05-01: On 1 May 2008, the fixed exchange rate with the US dollar was changed from USD 1 = TMM 6,250 to USD 1 = TMM 14,250; calculated devaluation: 56,1%.
Comment on 2008-12-31: Currency conversion with effect from 1 January 2009 at the rate of TMM 5,000 = TMT 1.
